{"tid":2286462,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★檢測中心---張先生：無香港身份證不能預約，覺得不合理","createTime":"2020-11-15T04:38:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T15:03:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5b8578c0829bc2a0b748f43ba53ddc5cbc59bb01","tid":2286462,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:38:34.000Z","msg":"市民陳小姐表示：「他(政府)說可以做檢測，可以過關，我爸爸媽媽八十多歲人 ，但一直封關未能回去(內地)，所以我很緊張，想做了(檢測)以後，我想回去探望父母，你這樣封關不是辦法。」  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被問到為何不預約前來，市民張先生稱：「因為我的兒子<span class=\"xx-large\">無香港身份證，他不能預約</span>，他們不設無香港身份證的預約，我想預約，我知道可以預約，但我做不到，只能夠提早八時來排隊，然後他們說要做完現場才做我們，覺得不合理。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5fb09a2b335d19664d51ba8d/政府社區檢測中心今起運作-有市民冀取證明後回內地探家人\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5fb09a2b335d19664d51ba8d%2F%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E4%BB%8A%E8%B5%B7%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C-%E6%9C%89%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%86%80%E5%8F%96%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E%E5%BE%8C%E5%9B%9E%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%8E%A2%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BBSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=e1d53568\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5fb09a2b335d19664d51ba8d/政府社區檢測中心今起運作-有市民冀取證明後回內地探家人</a>"},{"pid":"e8ac173a5365638f5c04ac23d8a8ace06b7c08a5","tid":2286462,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YYnUVPf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYYnUVPf.png&h=373765b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/joDkRnC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjoDkRnC.png&h=9188b2a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQWVFf0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQWVFf0.png&h=88b62a50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00b1a44d38abc694caa2911293e6efcfb1f29351","tid":